'''List of Shikinaisha in Suō Province''' (周防国の式内社一覧) is a list of {{ill|Shikinai shrines|de|Shikinai-Schreine|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|zh|式内神社}}, the shrines recorded in volumes 9 and 10 of the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|ja|延喜式神名帳|zh|延喜式神名帳}}, that are categorized under {{ill|Suō Province|de|Provinz Suō|ja|周防国|zh|周防国}}.
Also included are {{ill|Shikigeisha|de|Shikigeisha|ja|式外社|zh|式外社}}, shrines known to have existed at the time the Engishiki Jinmyōchō was compiled, but which are not listed in that document.
