Also included are {{ill|Shikigeisha|de|Shikigeisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|式外社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|13=User:Immanuelle/Shikigeisha|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 延喜式神名帳|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}, shrines known to have existed at the time the Engishiki Jinmyōchō was compiled, but which are not listed in that document.
